      "pageid": 5792,
      "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div id=\"infoboxborder\" style=\"float:right;display:block;\">\n<table>\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><b>Shed</b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;\"><b>Big Shed</b>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<th><a href=\"/File:Shed.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shed.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/15/Shed.png/96px-Shed.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"96\" height=\"110\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/15/Shed.png/144px-Shed.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/15/Shed.png/192px-Shed.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th><a href=\"/File:Big_Shed.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Big Shed.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d0/Big_Shed.png/96px-Big_Shed.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"96\" height=\"110\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d0/Big_Shed.png/144px-Big_Shed.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d0/Big_Shed.png/192px-Big_Shed.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"4\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Information\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Description\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0; width: 130px; line-height: 1.5;\"><i>An empty building. Fill it with whatever you like! The interior can be decorated.</i>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0; width: 130px; line-height: 1.5;\"><i>Doubles the size of the shed. The interior can be decorated.</i>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Upgrades From\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\">N/A\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\">Shed\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Building Cost\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"15000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />15,000g</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"><span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"20000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />20,000g</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr style=\"vertical-align:top;\">\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Building Materials\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"><style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r120955\">.mw-parser-output .nametemplate{margin:2px 5px 1px 2px;display:block;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline{margin:2px 0 1px 2px;display:inline;white-space:nowrap}.mw-parser-output .nametemplate img,.mw-parser-output .nametemplateinline img{max-width:none}</style><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(300)</span>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Wood.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/24px-Wood.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/df/Wood.png/36px-Wood.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/df/Wood.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Wood\" title=\"Wood\">Wood</a>&#160;(550)</span><link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r120955\"/><span class=\"nametemplate\"><img alt=\"Stone.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/24px-Stone.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/d/d4/Stone.png/36px-Stone.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/d/d4/Stone.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Stone\" title=\"Stone\">Stone</a>&#160;(300)</span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\">Footprint\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"><b>7x3</b><br /><a href=\"/File:Marker7x3.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Marker7x3.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0c/Marker7x3.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"111\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td>\n<td style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"><b>7x3</b><br /><a href=\"/File:Marker7x3.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Marker7x3.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0c/Marker7x3.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"111\" height=\"48\" /></a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<p>The <b>Shed</b> is a type of <a href=\"/Carpenter%27s_Shop#Farm_Buildings\" title=\"Carpenter&#39;s Shop\">farm building</a> purchasable from <a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a> at the <a href=\"/Carpenter%27s_Shop\" title=\"Carpenter&#39;s Shop\">Carpenter's Shop</a>. A shed can also be upgraded to a Big Shed at the Carpenter's Shop. To upgrade this building fully it would cost <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"35000\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />35,000g</span>. If purchasing the materials, it would cost <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"49500\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />49,500g</span> during year 1 or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"107500\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />107,500g</span> during year 2+.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Behavior\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Behavior</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Interior\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Interior</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Behavior\">Behavior</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Shed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Behavior\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Sheds act like small farmhouses, allowing players a room inside to decorate however they'd like with <a href=\"/Furniture\" title=\"Furniture\">furniture</a>, <a href=\"/Wallpaper\" title=\"Wallpaper\">wallpaper</a>, and <a href=\"/Flooring\" title=\"Flooring\">flooring</a>. The exterior is 7x3, smaller than its unupgraded 11x9 interior. The interior of the upgraded Big Shed is 17x12. This allows the player to effectively redistribute space on the farm.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Interior\">Interior</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Shed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Interior\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The initial interior of the shed is bare. The interior dimensions of the shed are 11x9, which is approximately the same size as the player's starting <a href=\"/Farmhouse\" title=\"Farmhouse\">farmhouse</a>. The Big Shed has dimensions of 17x12, providing slightly more than twice the area of the starting shed.\n</p><p>Note that the \"optimal layout\" images below apply to mouse/keyboard. Equipment in the corners usually cannot be reached when using a controller.\n</p>\n<ul class=\"gallery mw-gallery-traditional\">\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Shed_Inside.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/42/Shed_Inside.png/107px-Shed_Inside.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"107\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/42/Shed_Inside.png/160px-Shed_Inside.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/4/42/Shed_Inside.png/214px-Shed_Inside.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The interior of a Shed.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:20px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Big_Shed_Inside.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Big_Shed_Inside.png/120px-Big_Shed_Inside.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"120\" height=\"110\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Big_Shed_Inside.png/180px-Big_Shed_Inside.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/c/ca/Big_Shed_Inside.png/240px-Big_Shed_Inside.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The interior of a Big Shed.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:15px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Optimal_shed_layout.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Optimal_shed_layout.png/106px-Optimal_shed_layout.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"106\" height=\"120\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Optimal_shed_layout.png/159px-Optimal_shed_layout.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/9/91/Optimal_shed_layout.png/212px-Optimal_shed_layout.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The optimal Shed layout provides 67 spaces.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:20px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Optimal_big_shed_layout.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/43/Optimal_big_shed_layout.png/120px-Optimal_big_shed_layout.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"120\" height=\"110\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/4/43/Optimal_big_shed_layout.png/180px-Optimal_big_shed_layout.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/4/43/Optimal_big_shed_layout.png/240px-Optimal_big_shed_layout.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The optimal Big Shed layout provides 137 spaces.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\" style=\"width: 155px\"><div style=\"width: 155px\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\" style=\"width: 150px;\"><div style=\"margin:21.5px auto;\"><a href=\"/File:Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/12/Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png/120px-Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"120\" height=\"107\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/12/Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png/180px-Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/12/Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png/240px-Optimal_Big_Shed_Layout_Iridium_Scythe.png 2x\" /></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">\n<p>The optimal Big Shed layout provides 168 spaces for <a href=\"/Garden_Pot\" title=\"Garden Pot\">Garden Pots</a> harvestable by <a href=\"/Iridium_Scythe\" title=\"Iridium Scythe\">Iridium Scythe</a>. Lights may be placed in the remaining inaccessible spaces.\n</p>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Shed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The optimal layout of an unupgraded shed provides 67 spaces, but sheds are not the only farm buildings that can be used purely for storage.  A <a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a> provides 90 spaces, and a Deluxe Barn provides 136 spaces. <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coops</a> and <a href=\"/Cabin\" title=\"Cabin\">Cabins</a> can also be used purely for storage. Cabins provide 42 spaces when unclaimed, 113 spaces after a single upgrade, and 351 spaces after two upgrades.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Shed&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.1\" title=\"Version History\">1.1</a>: Introduced.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.3.36\" title=\"Version History\">1.3.36</a>: Doorway centered.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Big Shed introduced.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\">Buildings\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Merchants\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Abandoned_House\" title=\"Abandoned House\">Abandoned House</a> • <a href=\"/Adventurer%27s_Guild\" title=\"Adventurer&#39;s Guild\">Adventurer's Guild</a> • <a href=\"/Blacksmith\" title=\"Blacksmith\">Blacksmith</a> • <a href=\"/Bookseller\" title=\"Bookseller\">Bookseller</a> • <a href=\"/Carpenter%27s_Shop\" title=\"Carpenter&#39;s Shop\">Carpenter's Shop</a> • <a href=\"/Casino\" title=\"Casino\">Casino</a> • <a href=\"/Desert_Trader\" title=\"Desert Trader\">Desert Trader</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Shop\" title=\"Fish Shop\">Fish Shop</a> • <a href=\"/Giant_Stump\" title=\"Giant Stump\">Giant Stump</a> • <a href=\"/Harvey%27s_Clinic\" title=\"Harvey&#39;s Clinic\">Harvey's Clinic</a> • <a href=\"/Ice_Cream_Stand\" title=\"Ice Cream Stand\">Ice Cream Stand</a> • <a href=\"/Island_Trader\" title=\"Island Trader\">Island Trader</a> • <a href=\"/JojaMart\" title=\"JojaMart\">JojaMart</a> • <a href=\"/Marnie%27s_Ranch\" title=\"Marnie&#39;s Ranch\">Marnie's Ranch</a> • <a href=\"/Oasis\" title=\"Oasis\">Oasis</a> • <a href=\"/Pierre%27s_General_Store\" title=\"Pierre&#39;s General Store\">Pierre's General Store</a> • <a href=\"/Qi%27s_Walnut_Room\" title=\"Qi&#39;s Walnut Room\">Qi's Walnut Room</a> • <a href=\"/The_Stardrop_Saloon\" title=\"The Stardrop Saloon\">The Stardrop Saloon</a> • <a href=\"/Traveling_Cart\" title=\"Traveling Cart\">Traveling Cart</a> • <a href=\"/Volcano_Dungeon#Shop\" title=\"Volcano Dungeon\">Volcano Dwarf</a> • <a href=\"/Wizard%27s_Tower\" title=\"Wizard&#39;s Tower\">Wizard's Tower</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Houses\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/1_River_Road\" title=\"1 River Road\">1 River Road</a> • <a href=\"/Trailer\" title=\"Trailer\">2 River Road</a> • <a href=\"/1_Willow_Lane\" title=\"1 Willow Lane\">1 Willow Lane</a> • <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a> • <a href=\"/Carpenter%27s_Shop\" title=\"Carpenter&#39;s Shop\">24 Mountain Road</a> • <a href=\"/Elliott%27s_Cabin\" title=\"Elliott&#39;s Cabin\">Elliott's Cabin</a> • <a href=\"/Farmhouse\" title=\"Farmhouse\">Farmhouse</a> • <a href=\"/Island_Farmhouse\" title=\"Island Farmhouse\">Island Farmhouse</a> • <a href=\"/Leah%27s_Cottage\" title=\"Leah&#39;s Cottage\">Leah's Cottage</a> • <a href=\"/Mayor%27s_Manor\" title=\"Mayor&#39;s Manor\">Mayor's Manor</a> • <a href=\"/Tent\" title=\"Tent\">Tent</a> • <a href=\"/Trailer\" title=\"Trailer\">Trailer</a> • <a href=\"/Treehouse\" title=\"Treehouse\">Treehouse</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Farm Buildings\n</th>\n<th>Farming\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Barn\" title=\"Barn\">Barn</a> • <a href=\"/Cabin\" title=\"Cabin\">Cabin</a> • <a href=\"/Coop\" title=\"Coop\">Coop</a> • <a href=\"/Fish_Pond\" title=\"Fish Pond\">Fish Pond</a> • <a href=\"/Greenhouse\" title=\"Greenhouse\">Greenhouse</a> • <a href=\"/Mill\" title=\"Mill\">Mill</a> • <a href=\"/Pet_Bowl\" title=\"Pet Bowl\">Pet Bowl</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Shed</a>  • <a href=\"/Silo\" title=\"Silo\">Silo</a> • <a href=\"/Slime_Hutch\" title=\"Slime Hutch\">Slime Hutch</a> • <a href=\"/Stable\" title=\"Stable\">Stable</a> • <a href=\"/Well\" title=\"Well\">Well</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Special\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Desert_Obelisk\" title=\"Desert Obelisk\">Desert Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Earth_Obelisk\" title=\"Earth Obelisk\">Earth Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Farm_Obelisk\" title=\"Farm Obelisk\">Farm Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Gold_Clock\" title=\"Gold Clock\">Gold Clock</a> • <a href=\"/Island_Obelisk\" title=\"Island Obelisk\">Island Obelisk</a> • <a href=\"/Junimo_Hut\" title=\"Junimo Hut\">Junimo Hut</a> • <a href=\"/Water_Obelisk\" title=\"Water Obelisk\">Water Obelisk</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Other Buildings\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Community_Center\" title=\"Community Center\">Community Center</a> • <a href=\"/Dog_Pen\" title=\"Dog Pen\">Dog Pen</a> • <a href=\"/Island_Field_Office\" title=\"Island Field Office\">Island Field Office</a> • <a href=\"/Joja_Warehouse\" title=\"Joja Warehouse\">Joja Warehouse</a> • <a href=\"/Movie_Theater\" title=\"Movie Theater\">Movie Theater</a> • <a href=\"/Museum\" title=\"Museum\">Museum</a> • <a href=\"/Spa\" title=\"Spa\">Spa</a> • <a href=\"/Witch%27s_Hut\" title=\"Witch&#39;s Hut\">Witch's Hut</a>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414123625\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.076 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.085 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3656/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 3482/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 253/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 4569/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   59.159      1 -total\n 55.26%   32.690      2 Template:Description\n 16.89%    9.990      3 Template:Name\n  6.35%    3.755      3 Template:History\n  5.75%    3.400      5 Template:Price\n  3.63%    2.150      3 Template:Version\n  2.69%    1.589      1 Template:NavboxBuildings\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:5792-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414123625 and revision id 191908\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "<div id=\"infoboxborder\" style=\"float:right;display:block;\">\n{|\n|-\n|\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''Shed'''\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|'''Big Shed'''\n|-\n|\n![[File:Shed.png|96px]]\n![[File:Big Shed.png|96px]]\n|-\n|colspan=\"4\" id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: center;\"|Information\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align: right;\"|Description\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0; width: 130px; line-height: 1.5;\"|''{{Description|Shed}}''\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0; width: 130px; line-height: 1.5;\"|''{{Description|Big Shed}}''\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Upgrades From\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|N/A\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|Shed\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Building Cost\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Price|15000}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Price|20000}}\n|-style=\"vertical-align:top;\"\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Building Materials\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|Wood|300}}\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|{{Name|Wood|550}}{{Name|Stone|300}}\n|-\n|id=\"infoboxsection\" style=\"text-align:right;\"|Footprint\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|'''7x3'''<br />[[File:Marker7x3.png]]\n|style=\"border-right: 1px solid #8DCAF0;\"|'''7x3'''<br />[[File:Marker7x3.png]]\n|}</div>\n\nThe '''Shed''' is a type of [[Carpenter's Shop#Farm Buildings|farm building]] purchasable from [[Robin]] at the [[Carpenter's Shop]]. A shed can also be upgraded to a Big Shed at the Carpenter's Shop. To upgrade this building fully it would cost {{Price|35000}}. If purchasing the materials, it would cost {{Price|49500}} during year 1 or {{Price|107500}} during year 2+.\n\n==Behavior==\nSheds act like small farmhouses, allowing players a room inside to decorate however they'd like with [[furniture]], [[wallpaper]], and [[flooring]]. The exterior is 7x3, smaller than its unupgraded 11x9 interior. The interior of the upgraded Big Shed is 17x12. This allows the player to effectively redistribute space on the farm.\n\n==Interior==\nThe initial interior of the shed is bare. The interior dimensions of the shed are 11x9, which is approximately the same size as the player's starting [[farmhouse]]. The Big Shed has dimensions of 17x12, providing slightly more than twice the area of the starting shed.\n\nNote that the \"optimal layout\" images below apply to mouse/keyboard. Equipment in the corners usually cannot be reached when using a controller.\n<gallery>\nShed Inside.png|The interior of a Shed.\nBig Shed Inside.png|The interior of a Big Shed.\nOptimal shed layout.png|The optimal Shed layout provides 67 spaces.\nOptimal big shed layout.png|The optimal Big Shed layout provides 137 spaces.\nOptimal Big Shed Layout Iridium Scythe.png|The optimal Big Shed layout provides 168 spaces for [[Garden Pot|Garden Pots]] harvestable by [[Iridium Scythe]]. Lights may be placed in the remaining inaccessible spaces.\n</gallery>\n\n==Notes==\nThe optimal layout of an unupgraded shed provides 67 spaces, but sheds are not the only farm buildings that can be used purely for storage.  A [[Barn]] provides 90 spaces, and a Deluxe Barn provides 136 spaces. [[Coop]]s and [[Cabin]]s can also be used purely for storage. Cabins provide 42 spaces when unclaimed, 113 spaces after a single upgrade, and 351 spaces after two upgrades.\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.1|Introduced.}}\n{{History|1.3.36|Doorway centered.}}\n{{History|1.4|Big Shed introduced.}}\n\n{{NavboxBuildings}}\n\n[[Category:Farm buildings]]\n\n[[de:Schuppen]]\n[[es:Cabaña]]\n[[fr:Cabanon]]\n[[it:Rimessa]]\n[[ja:納屋]]\n[[ko:헛간]]\n[[hu:Raktár]]\n[[pt:Galpão]]\n[[ru:Сарай]]\n[[tr:Baraka]]\n[[zh:小屋]]"
    }
